Define the incremental fractional Brownian field $B_{H}(s+\tau)-B_{H}(s),
H\in (0,1)$, where $B_{H}(s)$ is a standard fractional Brownian motion with
Hurst index $H\in(0,1)$. In this paper we derive the exact asymptotic behaviour
of the maximum $\max_{(\tau,s)\in[0,1]\times[0,T]} (B_{H}(s+\tau)-B_{H}(s)) $
for any $H\in (0,1/2)$ complimenting thus the result of Zholud (2008) for the
Brownian motion.